long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
All the best websites on the internet organized on your homepage.

Speeds up your web browsing by setting CENTPAGE to open in New Tab page. Allows easy and quick access to all popular and your favorite websites including news, video, shopping, email, sports and more.

CENTPAGE is your all-in-one internet homepage or startpage. Use it as your homepage to save your time and enhance your productivity.
